- `src/main/java/{{ base_package | replace('.', '/') }}/service/`: use-case orchestration and transaction boundaries
- `src/main/java/{{ base_package | replace('.', '/') }}/domain/`: domain entities, enums, and invariant-bearing logic
- `src/main/java/{{ base_package | replace('.', '/') }}/repository/`: persistence adapters and Spring Data repositories
- `src/main/java/{{ base_package | replace('.', '/') }}/security/`: auth filters, converters, and security configuration
